{"TopicId":11741,"ForumId":32,"TopicTitle":"Lights on baby!!","CreatedByName":"TheProdigy","CreatedById":15985,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-05-31T02:09:47Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"TheProdigy","CreatedById":15985,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-05-31T02:09:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EWell, ive always felt like i was missing something in my night launches so i asked me self...whats missiing?\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E.........\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E......\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E...\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ELIGHT!!!!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ESo i said\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003ELETS LIGHT THIS BABY UP!!!\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/a79cd.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022a79cd.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/QTNiZ.png\u0022 alt=\u0022QTNiZ.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/LydGA.png\u0022 alt=\u0022LydGA.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EJust using good ol Cart mod...I was first using the Flood light mod, but they werent at the proper angles to light up the launch vehicle. So i just used these.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI had the idea to make light towers to get them to light up the tower proprely...but didnt work out (hard to move them and flipped over countless times)\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/boL5H.png\u0022 alt=\u0022boL5H.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Bluejayek","CreatedById":18471,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-05-31T02:16:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ENice stuff \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"togfox","CreatedById":17083,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-05-31T02:34:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EVery good. I assume you maneuvered them manually? Care to share the craft file and mod list?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-05-31T02:37:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EShoulda said, \u0027Let there be light!\u0027\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"OptimusSubPrime","CreatedById":9379,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-05-31T03:11:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EHow do you get that UI? \u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Phoxtane","CreatedById":6626,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-05-31T03:43:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022OptimusSubPrime\u0022 data-cite=\u0022OptimusSubPrime\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Cp\u003EHow do you get that UI? \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003ENew feature .15. Some parts will have a right-click menu that will show you some of their stats - in this case, how many units of fuel are left.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Thobewill10","CreatedById":6148,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-05-31T03:43:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThat\\\u0027s phenomenal. I must set something similar up.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"samstarman5","CreatedById":12469,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-05-31T09:43:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThere have been those who have said that night launches are quite possibly the best and most beautiful part of working a space program. I couldn\\\u0027t agree more. I do hope Squad has something in mind to make this more permanent.\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}